<h2>What Is Diverticulitis?<strong>
</strong></h2>
In this condition, small pouches appear inside the intestine in your body. These are known as diverticula. This can happen in many people and sometimes, these pouches do not lead to serious health hazards. However, in some instances, the pouches can turn inflamed and painful. This condition is referred as diverticulitis.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][vc_widget_sidebar sidebar_id="healthy_nutrition___food_sidebar"][/vc_column][/vc_row]";s:10:"post_title";s:29:"A to Z Of Diverticulitis Diet";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:29:"a-to-z-of-diverticulitis-diet";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-04-20 12:09:27";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-04-20 12:09:27";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:41:"http://localhost/homemadesolutions/?p=582";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}}